  "description": "Tree Vein Miner Removes entire trees (logs and leaves) when crouching",
  "body": "<h1 align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support me-Patreon-ff424d?logo=patreon&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/8GydmUN3xq\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Join our Discord-5865F2?logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Join our Discord\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support me-Ko--fi-571db5?logo=kofi&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\">\n  </a>\n</h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/cw/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/49b1e899a9f41e7eeeb877bc53e8d5838998a95b_0.webp\" alt=\"Patreon\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n# Tree Miner\n\nA Minecraft datapack that automatically chops down entire trees when you break a log while crouching.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/wEhW4ceB/images/32390c308957b4fd88e0a12083649cd56b1ce576.gif\" alt=\"Tree Miner Preview\">\n</p>\n\n## Notes\n\n- The tree miner only activates when you're crouching (sneaking)\n- Break logs normally without crouching if you only want to break one block\n- Leaves drop their normal items (saplings, sticks) just like breaking them manually\n- There's a small cooldown between uses to prevent performance issues",
